snippet.title: Fish - Atari 2600 (newly discovered prototype!)
snippet.description:
This never released Atari 2600 game, originally written in 1983, was just discovered on an Atari VAX/VMS backup tape and released to the public.  It's so amazing that we are still finding original Atari games 40+ years after they were created!  Thanks so much to Dutchman2000 and the folks at AtariAge for this magnificent find!  Most importantly, it's a great game and so much fun to play!

The game can be downloaded here and played on any sort of Atari 2600 emulation system:https://forums.atariage.com/topic/378560-new-game-discovered-for-the-2600-and-released-fish/
